    title: 'Skytest.ai: Smarter Automated Testing',
    body: 'With Skytest.ai, our AI-driven bots automate regression and end-to-end testing, adapting to changes in UI and APIs so issues are detected before they reach production. However, it\'s our QA specialists who design the right test coverage, interpret reports, and ensure that automated tests align with your most critical business needs.',
    link: { href: 'https://skytest.ai/', text: 'Skytest.ai' },
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M176 0V16 64h64V16 0h32V16 64h64V16 0h32V16 64h48 32V96v48h48 16v32H496 448v64h48 16v32H496 448v64h48 16v32H496 448v48 32H416 368v48 16H336V496 448H272v48 16H240V496 448H176v48 16H144V496 448H96 64V416 368H16 0V336H16 64V272H16 0V240H16 64V176H16 0V144H16 64V96 64H96h48V16 0h32zM416 96H96V416H416V96zm-96 80h32v16V320v16H320V320 192 176zM135.9 336l2.2-5.7L160 272.8V272h.3l32.7-85.7L197 176h22l3.9 10.3L255.7 272h.3v.8l21.9 57.5 2.2 5.7H245.9l-12.2-32H182.3l-12.2 32H135.9zM208 236.8L194.6 272h26.9L208 236.8z"/></svg>`,
    title: 'AI-Assisted Coding',
    body: "Our developers leverage AI coding assistants to enhance productivity, accelerating code writing, review, and optimization. However, robust applications demand more than code generation. Our engineers ensure every line adheres to Oursky's rigorous standards for quality, security, and maintainability.",
  },
];

